---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 搜索
description: 搜索博客文章
---

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">搜索</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">在博客中搜索你感兴趣的内容</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 搜索框 -->
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
    <div class="relative">
      <input 
        type="text" 
        id="searchInput" 
        placeholder="输入关键词搜索..." 
        class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-lg border-2 border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 focus:border-livingCoral focus:outline-none transition-colors"
      >
      <div class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-neutral-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 搜索结果 -->
  <div id="searchResults" class="space-y-6">
    <!-- 搜索结果将在这里动态显示 -->
  </div>

  <!-- 无结果提示 -->
  <div id="noResults" class="hidden text-center py-12">
    <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto text-neutral-300 dark:text-neutral-600 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.172 16.172a4 4 0 015.656 0M9 12h6m-6-4h6m2 5.291A7.962 7.962 0 0112 15c-2.34 0-4.47-.881-6.08-2.33"></path>
    </svg>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">没有找到相关结果</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">尝试使用其他关键词或检查拼写</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 搜索提示 -->
  <div id="searchTips" class="text-center py-8 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
    <p>输入关键词开始搜索，支持标题、内容、标签和分类搜索</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 搜索索引数据 -->
<script>
  window.searchIndex = [
    {% for item in collections.searchIndex %}
    {
      "title": "{{ item.title | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
      "description": "{{ item.description | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
      "tags": [{% for tag in item.tags %}"{{ tag }}"{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}{% endfor %}],
      "category": "{{ item.category | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
      "date": "{{ item.date }}",
      "url": "{{ item.url }}",
      "excerpt": "{{ item.excerpt | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
      "cover": "{{ item.cover | replace('"', '\\"') }}"
    }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  ];
</script>

<!-- 搜索脚本 -->
<script src="{{ '/assets/search.js' | url }}"></script>
